{"tid":2127501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃永幾時收皮","createTime":"2020-07-27T10:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T05:00:46.000Z","uid":137043,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"d92754a4ffa8ebaf04629f8f44f7ddeb33da5ddf","tid":2127501,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"家母最鐘意聽住電台做嘢<br />\n依家又咁啱播緊黃永個唔知咩節目<br />\n一開波就大大聲屌香港人自己搞到日日百幾單肺炎<br />\n話民主派最鐘意屌政府抗疫不足<br />\n但又唔反思自己有幾唔掂，咩都推比政府<br />\n個男partner仲話係我哋太自由先會搞到咁嚴重<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲唔聽話嘅香港人當然要屌<br />\n但做得最差、最有責任嘅一定係政府<br />\n一早講咗唔可以免檢疫、封關<br />\n偏偏唔做，所以先keep住有帶毒者入到嚟播毒<br />\n專家都話好大機會係由免檢疫人士導致第三波發生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你條閪屌就鳩up，一句車埋嚟屌哂全港<br />\n政府有錯就一句不提？<br />\n屌自己人就最撚落力<br />\n黃永幾時收皮唔好再岀聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8bc26380a26dde06b0a3e3276d512339ec8e8b","tid":2127501,"uid":13308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"人民大道中=大大力屌泛民, 細細聲屌政府"},{"pid":"31ab091de086e542f7c64d4457bc9b18cc6cabaf","tid":2127501,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"當年俾民建聯做節目就係佢"},{"pid":"10a8d608e7681dfa4740cc5f03248543d876de36","tid":2127501,"uid":28155,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"屌自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583edb4ae6229abd24d28686c32224c06733e212","tid":2127501,"uid":20170,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3e8bc26380a26dde06b0a3e3276d512339ec8e8b","tid":2127501,"uid":13308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"人民大道中=大大力屌泛民, 細細聲屌政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"人民大道中=大大力屌泛民, <span class=\"red\">大大聲讚政府</span>"},{"pid":"56b70aacdb3f7683fe5b6be39fb5008f308082a4","tid":2127501,"uid":37528,"like":